{"tid":1802143,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"Afk arena (17) 2019 最佛心既手機game","createTime":"2019-12-29T08:23:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T08:49:59.000Z","uid":152500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"498fd815422c15903607aefc9be5e212a72a585c","tid":1802143,"uid":152500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T08:23:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EVK55t5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEVK55t5.jpg&h=cfbfb7f4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rx9eenq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRx9eenq.jpg&h=18ba26e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAFK Arena 係一隻掛機升呢養老驚，如果想瘋狂沉醉係呢驚度，sorry你可以上一頁<br />\n呢隻驚偏歐美畫風 放置類手機驚，似放置英雄/奇兵玩法<br />\n巴打評價：<br />\n<br />\n唔使肝/平衡好/獎勵多/副本針對大眾<br />\n0課、輕課、中課無大分別，只有極重課可大幅拉開距離<br />\n<br />\n評分都幾高 核心玩法其實都係差不多 但又唔係一成不變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n關於健檢<br />\n<br />\n其實個人認為在湊齊五白之前，真的不需要所謂健檢，個人玩到目前22章，只要照著女妖遠征的節奏，都是不需要健檢直接推過，簡單說就是等級，人物等級到了自然就過了<br />\n<br />\n五白之後，或者是更後面的章節，等級開始突破240以上，這時才是真正該健檢的時候<br />\n<br />\n前面的章節1x章甚至22章以前，推不過都是只有一個原因，您的角色等級不夠，等級夠了自然就過了，如果要極限推圖，yt上面很多章節攻略文，上來發健檢文其實真的沒多大意義，谷哥一下會比你上來發問來得快很多<br />\n<br />\n種族選擇<br />\n<br />\n無課，奈米課，微課，唯一選擇都是耀光<br />\n<br />\n耀光是目前四大種族無論是屬性互補，傷害，控場，續航，最完整的一個種族<br />\n<br />\n只要您是在微課以下，代表您的資源一定會不夠，遠征其實就是在比誰能夠將資源最大化，就能夠走得更遠<br />\n<br />\n當然，如果您對特定種族有愛，那當然另當別論，畢竟遊戲就是要讓自己開心的<br />\n<br />\n新手組隊： 161前<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W1Zaw7F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW1Zaw7F.png&h=462bea34&s={SIZE}\" />+<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xii6PUp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxii6PUp.png&h=20d60524&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n161後：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ouDq5sW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FouDq5sW.png&h=416f0581&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n裝備強化: <br />\n呢隻驚強裝係好公道，裝食裝係100%點數回饋而且計埋本身裝備值既點數俾你。有鎚仔幣不仿卡關時先去沖一沖裝再去打副本(需要充足既錢幣)<br />\n可推薦前期升裝(不建議升藍裝)(詳程可睇返&quot;水晶石介紹&quot;)<br />\nps:鼓勵裝備升到二星就夠,綠裝不能強化<br />\n<br />\n首抽：<br />\n呢隻game唔洗del完再開重抽，轉ser即可重抽，按你profile pic-&gt;Setting就可轉ser<br />\n<br />\n課金:<br />\n想課金巴打要留意!!記得要轉繁體中文先可以到google play俾錢!!(設定&gt;語言)<br />\n推薦課金禮金: <br />\n158經濟過關包&gt;皇令/迷宮令&gt;118窮撚月卡包&gt;月卡&gt;種族塔禮包&gt; all 禮包<br />\n<br />\nTier-list<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.afkarena.net/tier-list\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.afkarena.net%2Ftier-list&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK92t2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=d115e3a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.afkarena.net/tier-list</a><br />\n公會: <br />\n有新手巴打要入會暫時得柒個公會。請在post留名/自行apply，不限任何ser都可以入會 (退會要1小時冷卻先可以再入會) <br />\n請自行搜索:lihkg/lihkg2/lihkg3/lihk4/lihkg5/ihkg6/lihkg7(消失的7會) /lihkg8/lihkg9<br />\nPs:(不知明的lihkg10會 暫時唔好入住 因未聯絡到會長可能假連登會) <br />\n內有完善既聊天系統(可以貼j圖) <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTier-list<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.afkarena.net/tier-list\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.afkarena.net%2Ftier-list&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK92t2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=d115e3a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.afkarena.net/tier-list</a>"},{"pid":"97f9c3cae3c569447c64415983fb52ad5cb99e91","tid":1802143,"uid":152500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T08:25:17.000Z","msg":"巴哈有好多齊全攻略文，歡迎新手去睇，有咩漏歡迎各位bro 再補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f412c6e71b618019c4b3148da89dfea0d1e4f30e","tid":1802143,"uid":152500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T08:41:52.000Z","msg":"關於角色:<br />\n隻game有6個族， 半神,惡魔,耀光,獸族,綠裔,亡靈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pKZ2onC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpKZ2onC.jpg&h=5080a9e0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dNQ1DVX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdNQ1DVX.jpg&h=d944dc1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁咩角色係原生紫卡呢， 簡單啲睇佢有幾招技，3招技即係肥料<br />\n<br />\n心願清單：放入心願清單的角色抽中機率高達9成，所以抽之前記得睇下自己清單<br />\n<br />\n半神同惡魔冇得放入心願清單，只能大海抽 ，占星獲得，亦稱課長先玩得起"},{"pid":"8aa360952f852f7f172ec73e98a895dbc2230e9a","tid":1802143,"uid":206691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T08:49:10.000Z","msg":"18喎爸打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"445a808c80a410a1fe79285a62190f6605542180","tid":1802143,"uid":152500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8aa360952f852f7f172ec73e98a895dbc2230e9a","tid":1802143,"uid":206691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T08:49:10.000Z","msg":"18喎爸打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T08:49:59.000Z","msg":"重新開左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}